      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54B32 power unit, featuring its signature individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing in peak operational condition. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with the rear subframe mounting points reinforced and documented. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Every bushing, damper, and control arm remains within factory tolerances, providing the telepathic steering feedback this platform is renowned for. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero oxidative degradation, while the interior preserves the tactile integrity of the original materials. This specimen is mechanically and aesthetically pristine, preserved for the discerning purist.",
